{{Infobox journal | cover = | discipline = [[Social sciences]], [[humanities]] | abbreviation =Magallania | editor = Flavia Morello R. | language = Spanish | publisher = [[University of Magallanes]] | country = Chile | history = 1970-present | frequency = Biannually | website = http://www.scielo.cl/scielo.php?script=sci_serial&pid=0718-2244&lng=en&nrm=iso | link1 = http://www.scielo.cl/scielo.php?script=sci_issues&pid=0718-2244&lng=en&nrm=iso | link1-name = Online archive | ISSN = 0718-0209 | eISSN = 0718-2244 | OCLC = 225866115 }} '''''Magallania''''' is an [[academic journal]] published by the [[University of Magallanes]]. It publishes articles on social sciences and humanities regarding [[Patagonia]], [[Tierra del Fuego]], and [[Antarctica]]. The journal was published annually from its establishment in 1970 until 2005 when it began to be issued twice a year.
